    <lb ed="T" n="0718b08"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0718b08"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><persName key="A000449">尊法</persName>傳</head><p>
        <lb ed="T" n="0718b09"/><persName key="A000449">釋尊法</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000055425">西印度</placeName>人也，梵云<persName key="A000449">伽梵達磨</persName>，華云
<lb ed="T" n="0718b10"/><persName key="A000449">尊法</persName>。遠踰沙磧，來抵<placeName key="PL000000000083">中華</placeName>，有傳譯之心，堅
        <lb ed="T" n="0718b11"/>化導之願。<persName key="A002146">天皇</persName><date from-iso="0650" key="j19585081960692" to-iso="0656">永徽之歲</date>，翻出《千手千眼觀
<lb ed="T" n="0718b12"/>世音菩薩廣大圓滿無礙大悲心陀羅尼經》一
<lb ed="T" n="0718b13"/>卷。經題但云<placeName key="PL000000055425">西天竺</placeName><persName key="A000449">伽梵達磨</persName>譯，不標年
<lb ed="T" n="0718b14"/>代。推其本末，疑是<date from-iso="0650" key="j19585081960692" to-iso="0656">永徽</date>、<date from-iso="0656" key="j19606931962582" to-iso="0661">顯慶</date>中也。又準《千
        <lb ed="T" n="0718b15"/>臂經序》云：「<persName key="A001275">智通</persName>同<ref type="person" target="#A000449"><anchor xml:id="beg0718002"/>此<anchor xml:id="end0718002"/>三藏</ref>譯也。」<ptr target="#n328"/><persName key="A000449">法</persName>後不
<lb ed="T" n="0718b16"/>知其終。</p>
